## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="4ed05-275">Im folgenden Beispiel wird die vom Synthesizer, um einen Ausdruck an, an die Standardausgabe audio zu sprechen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4ed05-275">The following example uses the synthesizer to speak a phrase to the default audio output.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
